These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: polish, colombian, spanish, nigerian, french, australian, chinese
1. the french is between the spanish and the colombian##2
2. the australian is on the right of the polish##1
3. the chinese is on the right of the nigerian##1
4. the australian is in the middle##1
5. the colombian is in an odd position##4
6. the spanish is on the left of the french##1
7. the polish is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3     |    4    |   5    |    6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | chinese | polish | australian | spanish | french | colombian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: skateboarding, skiing, rowing, ice-hockey, tennis, cricket, cycling
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2     |   3    |    4     |    5    |  6   |     7      |
| Sport   | tennis | skateboarding | cricket | skiing | ice-hockey | rowing | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-3::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  journalist, scientist, nurse, accountant, entrepreneur, police-officer, dressmaker
1. the nurse is on the right of the dressmaker##1
2. the journalist is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
3. the scientist is on the left or right of the accountant##3
4. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
5. the accountant is on the left of the journalist##1
6. the journalist is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
7. the nurse is in an even position##4
8. the journalist is on the left of the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |   2   |      3      |         4          |      5       |     6     |    7    |
| Job   | scientist | accountant | journalist | entrepreneur | dressmaker | nurse | police-officer |

