.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: sailing, badminton, basketball, skateboarding, weightlifting, snowboarding, climbing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
3. the person who's sport is basketball is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3     |    4     |   5    |     6      |  7   |
| Sport   | sailing | climbing | skateboarding | snowboarding | weightlifting | basketball | badminton |

