.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-5::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: juice, 7up, tea, soy-milk, almond-milk, cola, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
6. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |    3    |    4     |   5   |   6   |   7    |
| Beverage   | 7up | soy-milk | almond-milk | tea | juice | hot-chocolate | cola |

