1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking sprite is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking sprite##2
6. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
7. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2    |    3     |  4  |   5   |    6     |   7    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | hot-chocolate | fanta | sprite | milk | juice | cola |

