.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-9::.
7 different pets are kept: pony, rat, ferret, hedgehog, guinea-pig, bird, mouse
1. the owner of the hedgehog is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
3. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
5. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
7. the owner of the mouse is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
9. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |   2   |     3      |   4    |   5    |  6   |   7   |
| Pet   | ferret | mouse | pony | guinea-pig | bird | rat | hedgehog |

