1. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
4. the fan of house is in the middle##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
6. the fan of d&b is in an even position##4
7. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |  3   |  4   |  5   |     6     |  7  |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | reggae | metal | house | electronic | d&b | disco |

