.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-13::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: snowmobile, bike, taxi, scooter, boat, helicopter, motorbike
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person driving the bike is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |  3   |   4    |   5   |  6  |  7  |
| Transport   | bike | scooter | boat | taxi | helicopter | motorbike | snowmobile |

