.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-20::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: helicopter, bus, train, car, scooter, roller, van
 1. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
 5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
 8. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |  2   |  3   |  4   |     5      |     6     |  7   |
| Transport   | bus | helicopter | van | car | scooter | train | roller |

 